text: The Roscosmos State Corporation for Space Activities,, Gosudarstvennaya korporatsiya po kosmicheskoy deyatyelnosti "Roskosmos". also known as Roscosmos (), is a state corporation of the Russian Federation. They focus on the country's space flights, cosmonautics programs, and aerospace research. ==Notes== ==References== Category:Space agencies Category:Organizations based in Russia
title: Roscosmos
